Package: folder-watcher
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libc6
Maintainer: Tae-Yeong Kwak <tykwak@deepbio.co.kr>
Description: A tool to watch folders and execute tasks automatically.
 This application monitors specified folders for new files. When a file is
 fully saved, it triggers a user-defined application or script.
 It provides a web interface for monitoring and management.